[SPEAKER_00] Onda dva put meki.

645
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, dva put meki.

646
00:42:02,860 --> 00:42:03,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, ajde.

647
00:42:03,860 --> 00:42:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ali samo jedan potpis.

648
00:42:05,860 --> 00:42:08,860
[SPEAKER_00] Boris na drugim srtić.

649
00:42:08,860 --> 00:42:10,860
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, može. Eto.

650
00:42:10,860 --> 00:42:12,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, Boris. Hvala ti.

651
00:42:12,860 --> 00:42:16,860
[SPEAKER_01] Baš je bilo lijepo ugodno da neko optimističan došao malo na kraju.

652
00:42:16,860 --> 00:42:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala što su me pozvali.

653
00:42:17,860 --> 00:42:18,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ma i drugi put.

654
00:42:18,860 --> 00:42:19,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ekipa ništa ono.

655
00:42:19,860 --> 00:42:21,860
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala, like, subscribe.

656
00:42:21,860 --> 00:42:23,860
[SPEAKER_01] Pratite i Borisa.

657
00:42:23,860 --> 00:42:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] Vidimo se.

658
00:42:24,860 --> 00:42:25,860
[SPEAKER_01] I share, share.

659
00:42:51,860 --> 00:42:52,659
[UNKNOWN] Hvala na sviđanju!

